The paper deals with image analysis, object detection, and scene text analysis, which are all related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep convolutional linear pyramids also suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.CL). The paper also mentions efforts to improve accuracy, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of learning machines and empirical selection of kernels suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
